post_survey.music_making: I played cello between the ages of 7 and 12 and sang in musicals from 14 to 18.
post_survey.activities: I put it in the background when I'm doing admin work like answering emails. I also use it when I'm walking or commuting.
post_survey.habit_change: I listened to a lot of classical music when I was younger and have definitely started listening to significantly more hip hop in recent years.
post_survey.habits: When I'm relaxing I put on folk/indie and when I'm working or commuting I put on alt rock and hip hop.
